<Base
  title="What Is a Good Cold Email Reply Rate? Benchmarks That Survived the Privacy Era"
  description="A good cold email campaign earns a 2–6% total reply rate, with 1–3% positive replies. Below 1% total signals a list, deliverability, or offer problem. Benchmarks from Sales.co platform data."
